HEADWORD: Bilection
<hw>Bi*lec"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>
<def>That portion of a group of moldings which projects beyond the
general surface of a panel; a bolection.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

